<br><br>
<br>Fought and destroyed hords of evils creatures. The remainder fled to <a data-href="Elszáradt" href="https://karlsayle.github.io/places/continents/elszáradt.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">Elszáradt</a>.
<br><br>
<br>The year 578 of the second age
<br><br>
<br>The good races united and systematically eradicated countless evil beings in a century long struggle to free the land of Földrend.
